  <prompt>
    Final project wrap-up — execute the mandatory wrap-up checklist: (1) run `/code-review` on all project code; (2) run `/adr-check`; (3) run `/repo-cleanup projects/smart-todo-decoupling-r3`; (4) update `README.md` Status → Complete + check all Graduation Criteria; (5) update `plan.md` Status → Complete + mark all phases ✅; (6) write `notes/lessons-learned.md` covering implementation surprises + decisions revised + advice for R4 (or follow-on projects); (7) final TASK-INDEX.md status check — every task ✅; (8) verify no critical code-review issues remain.
  </prompt>

  <role>Spaarke project closer.</role>

  <goal>Project marked Complete with all graduation criteria verified. Lessons-learned written. Repo clean. No critical code-review issues.</goal>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="task-create §3.7">Mandatory wrap-up steps: quality gates → repo-cleanup → README → plan → lessons-learned → verification.</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>.claude/skills/code-review/SKILL.md</file>
      <file>.claude/skills/adr-check/SKILL.md</file>
      <file>.claude/skills/repo-cleanup/SKILL.md</file>
