      <file>projects/smart-todo-decoupling-r3/plan.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Run `/code-review` against all project-touched code. Fix any critical issues identified. Re-run until clean.</step>
    <step order="2">Run `/adr-check` against all project code. Fix any ADR violations. Re-run until clean.</step>
    <step order="3">Run `/repo-cleanup projects/smart-todo-decoupling-r3` to audit + remove ephemeral files. Review the cleanup report; approve removals (notes/debug, notes/spikes, notes/drafts). Archive handoffs if any.</step>
    <step order="4">Update `README.md`: Status → Complete; Last Updated → today; Phase → Complete; Progress → 100%; Completed Date filled; all Graduation Criteria checked.</step>
    <step order="5">Update `plan.md`: Status → Complete; mark every phase Deliverable as ✅.</step>
    <step order="6">Write `projects/smart-todo-decoupling-r3/notes/lessons-learned.md`: implementation surprises, decisions revised vs. original spec, tooling gotchas, advice for follow-on projects (especially Microsoft Planner integration if reconsidered, Outlook v2 with edit flow, mobile-native deferred work).</step>
    <step order="7">Verify TASK-INDEX.md: every task marked ✅.</step>
    <step order="8">Final smoke test: BFF boots cleanly with feature flag both ON and OFF; SmartTodo loads + queries `sprk_todo`; Outlook ribbon + indicator work; round-trip sync round-trips within 60s.</step>
    <step order="9">Add a Changelog entry in `README.md` marking completion.</step>
    <step order="10">Update TASK-INDEX.md status to ✅ completed for this task.</step>
  </steps>

  <outputs>
    <output type="docs">`README.md` Status → Complete</output>
    <output type="docs">`plan.md` Status → Complete; phases ✅</output>
    <output type="docs">`projects/smart-todo-decoupling-r3/notes/lessons-learned.md`</output>
    <output type="docs">`projects/smart-todo-decoupling-r3/tasks/TASK-INDEX.md` (all ✅)</output>
